data.name: unpackingRichTextBox.Text
data.value:
Unpacking: - Choose Taz Pak files (pc, xpb, ps2) on the first file dialog and output folder the on second - Make sure you have at least 1 GB free memory space if you want unpack all files - This process can take some time ... - Use specific tools to open and edit unpacked media files: Audacity (raw 11025 Hz), Foobar2000 + vgmstream plugin, Raw bitmap editors, etc...
